{"tid":1307090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蕭若元：支持示威者圍蝦疑似女警的人是法西斯～ 示威還示威者，請不要成為垃圾人。","createTime":"2019-07-11T11:52:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T13:32:06.000Z","uid":219007,"like":2,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"84e0b0860ed535ec2c2d6b7c148dc1ecd56fe339","tid":1307090,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T11:52:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Fuil55_yexY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFuil55_yexY&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWjnyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=e50e3597\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Fuil55_yexY</a><br />\n<br />\n如果那位疑似女警影你相再公開最多都係侵犯私隱，並沒有刑事成份。<br />\n<br />\n但蕭生睇完條片，見示威者圍住咁樣對付一個女人，無論佢係藍絲或警察，咁對人就係不當！<br />\n<br />\n藍絲甚樣對你，警察甚樣對你就可以甚樣對返人？想利用別人的不當來合理化自己的不當行為？這就是只問立場不問是非。這亦是中國羅輯。<br />\n<br />\n做人要識分事非黑白，絶不能因為你係黃絲就義不容辭地支持，而藍絲一定係錯，凡事都要睇證據。相反，如果凡事以立埸先行去判斷，就會與法西斯納粹一樣。<br />\n<br />\n 示威提醒，請不要成為垃圾人。"},{"pid":"a2a12a4c995239985971b05eb330c1788020e87f","tid":1307090,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T11:53:56.000Z","msg":"燒山講就叻 出來示範比大家睇啦"},{"pid":"c9ace2a93206d6a4f79fbbd1d75896a42c9ea09a","tid":1307090,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T11:54:08.000Z","msg":"【任務欄】<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1306215\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1306215</a><br />\n任務眾多，請自行因應人數及背後目的考慮做邊D任 ；黃色為主線任務；紅色係Boss <br />\n7.11 - 梁烈士公眾告別禮 - <a href=\"http://t.me/leung711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fleung711&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWjnyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=e1fe6a4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/leung711</a><br />\n7.11 - 油尖旺區議會夢遊 - <a href=\"http://t.me/ytm_dc711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fytm_dc711&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWjnyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=21c6d14a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/ytm_dc711</a><br />\n7.12 - 6.12一周月行動 - <a href=\"https://www.facebook.co